<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 25 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange closed at 1763.52 on Saturday, down 2.83
points from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 851,935 shares changed hands in 650 deals, and the
turnover was 2.77 billion rials (about 920,000 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
In the trading, shares of 27 companies made gains, and those of
19 others declined. 
</P>
</TEXT>
