<HEADLINE> China to Strengthen Party Leadership of SOEs (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Decision says that Party organizations in enterprises
should carry out the Party's basic line in earnest, center their
attention on production and operation, and serve for the
fulfillment of the Party's tasks and enterprise reform and
development.
</P>
<P>
Non-stop efforts should be made to improve the work of the
Party organizations and the ways they carry out activities, and
further explore channels and methods to bring into play their
political role as the core.
</P>
<P>
Steps must be taken to strengthen and improve ideological and
political education in enterprises, unite the workers with the
common ideal of building socialism with Chinese characteristics,
guiding them to actively support and participate in China's reform
drive, and whole-heartedly help them solve actual difficulties.
The Party organizations in loss-incurring and merged or bankrupt
enterprises, in particular, should conduct thoroughgoing and
painstaking ideological work among workers and staff members.
</P>
<P>
Party committees and governments at all levels should firmly
stand at the forefront of the SOE reform drive, emancipate their
minds, be practical and realistic, follow the objective economic
law and respect the masses' pioneering spirit.
</P>
<P>
Earnest steps should be taken to improve the leading styles and,
starting from the actual situation of SOEs of various trades, to
make thorough investigations and studies, starting from the actual
situation of SOEs of various trades, summarize new experience,
study new situations, and solve newly arising problems, and unite
with and lead officials and the people in general to overcome
difficulties and press ahead.  
</P>
